libgbt
======

A Bittorrent library robust like a grizzly

The Grizzly BitTorrent library (will) implement all the functionality
described in the bittorrent protocol RFC[0], as well as the distributed
hash table (DHT) protocol[1].

Installation
------------
Edit the `config.mk` file to match your setup, then run:

	$ make
	# make install

Usage
-----
Include the header file as follow:

	#include <libgtb.h>

Link your program against it with

	cc pgm.c -lgbt -o pgm

Until v1.0 is complete, please check the `libgbt.h` for the API.

